task.summary: 0.9.0 - Initial commit for all branches (added Matrix Mode template)
0.9.1 - Setup architecture for Graphing in Function Mode
0.9.2 - Finished basic graphing ability; still required testing, debugging and improving
0.10.1 - Added cursors and side scrolling architecture
Beta 2.0 - Bug Fixes; Commit for Round 2 of testing
Beta 3.0 - Bug Fixes; Commit for Round 3 of testing
1.9 - Improvements to JFok Algorithm for processing decimal fractions, displaying fractions, and scalars of vector equations
1.99 - With slight bug fixes, display upgrades and changes in themes
2.4 Overall Merge with 5 Themes, Updated Constants and Completed Matrix Mode
